$1 {without the c1-square avilable, Ivanisevic finds another way to put the
rook on the c-file} Kf8 {Black is forced to play this way} (18... O-O $2 19.
Bxf5 $1 {wins either the h4 or the d5-pawn}) 19. Rc2 Kg7 20. Kh2 Nb6 21. Nc3
Bb4 22. cxd5 cxd5 23. Nb5 $5 Rxc2 24. Bxc2 Rc8 25. Bd3 $14 {White's position
